name: Buy Now! Going Fast!
description:
You are trying to buy a ticket to an upcoming concert. The website is going live any minute now. So, you keep refreshing, to be sure you can claim your ticket, even though it is currently returning a 404 error...

Notes:
- This game does have an ending :) It is about perhaps 10-20 minutes long?

- Make sure your sound is on

- The sound may be a little loud, I do not know anything about mastering. Make sure you have your volume knob ready if it's too loud (or too quiet!)
